# Normalize line endings to LF in the repository.
# The project is edited on both Mac and Windows (it lives on OneDrive), and
# without this every Windows checkout rewrites files with CRLF, so they show
# up as dirty forever with no real content change. Forcing LF in the repo
# keeps diffs honest and stops that phantom churn.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets: never touch their bytes.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.pdf binary
